"The :guilabel:`Extra CSS` option allows you to specify arbitrary CSS that "
"will be applied to all HTML files in the input. This CSS is applied with "
"very high priority and so should override most CSS present in the **input "
"document** itself. You can use this setting to fine tune the "
"presentation/layout of your document. For example, if you want all "
"paragraphs of class `endnote` to be right aligned, just add::"
