msgid ""
"This expression is rather complex, because it tries to handle a number of "
"common cases simultaneously. What it means is that calibre will assume "
"chapters start at either `<h1>` or `<h2>` tags that have any of the words "
"`(chapter, book, section or part)` in them or that have the "
