#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:618
msgid "From the defaults set in Preferences->Conversion"
msgstr "源自“首选项 -> 转换”中设置的默认值"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:620
msgid ""
"From the saved conversion settings for each book being converted (if any). "
"This can be turned off by the option in the top left corner of the Bulk "
"conversion dialog."
