#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:659
msgid ""
"calibre will automatically generate a Table of Contents based on headings if"
" you mark your headings with the ``Heading 1``, ``Heading 2``, etc. styles "
"in Microsoft Word. Open the output e-book in the calibre E-book viewer and "
"click the :guilabel:`Table of Contents` button to view the generated Table "
"of Contents."
msgstr "如果您在 Microsoft Word 中将标题标记为“标题 1”、“标题 2”等样式，calibre 将根据这些标题自动生成目录。在 calibre 电子书阅读器中打开输出的电子书，点击 :guilabel:`目录` 按钮即可查看生成的目录。"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:665
msgid "Older .doc files"
