msgstr ":guilabel:`段落样式: Auto`"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:688
msgid ""
"Analyzes the text file and attempts to automatically determine how "
"paragraphs are defined.  This option will generally work fine, if you "
"achieve undesirable results try one of the manual options."
msgstr "分析文本文件并尝试自动确定段落的定义方式。该选项通常运行良好，如果结果不尽如人意，请尝试使用某种手动选项。"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:691
msgid ":guilabel:`Paragraph style: Block`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`段落样式: Block`"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:692
msgid "Assumes one or more blank lines are a paragraph boundary::"
msgstr "假设一个或多个空行即为段落分界线::"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:699
msgid ":guilabel:`Paragraph style: Single`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`段落样式: Single`"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:700
msgid "Assumes that every line is a paragraph::"
msgstr "假设每一行都是一个独立的段落::"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:706
msgid ":guilabel:`Paragraph style: Print`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`段落样式: Print`"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:707
msgid ""
"Assumes that every paragraph starts with an indent (either a tab or 2+ "
"spaces). Paragraphs end when the next line that starts with an indent is "
"reached::"
msgstr "假设每个段落都以缩进开头（制表符或 2 个以上的空格）。当遇到下一个以缩进开头的行时，当前段落结束::"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:717
msgid ":guilabel:`Paragraph style: Unformatted`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`段落样式: Unformatted`"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:718
msgid ""
"Assumes that the document has no formatting, but does use hard line breaks."
"  Punctuation and median line length are used to attempt to re-create "
"paragraphs."
msgstr "假设文档没有任何格式设置，但使用了硬换行符。系统将通过标点符号和平均行长度来尝试重新构建段落。"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:721
msgid ":guilabel:`Formatting style: Auto`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`格式化样式:自动`"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:722
msgid ""
"Attempts to detect the type of formatting markup being used.  If no markup "
"is used then heuristic formatting will be applied."
msgstr "尝试检测正在使用的格式标记类型。如果未检测到任何标记，则将应用“智能处理”。"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:725
msgid ":guilabel:`Formatting style: Heuristic`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`格式化样式:智能`"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:726
msgid ""
"Analyzes the document for common chapter headings, scene breaks, and "
"italicized words and applies the appropriate HTML markup during conversion."
msgstr "分析文档中的常见章节标题、分节符以及斜体词汇，并在转换过程中应用相应的 HTML 标记。"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:729
msgid ":guilabel:`Formatting style: Markdown`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`格式化样式: Markdown`"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:730
msgid ""
"calibre also supports running TXT input though a transformation preprocessor"
" known as Markdown. Markdown allows for basic formatting to be added to TXT "
"documents, such as bold, italics, section headings, tables, lists, a Table "
"of Contents, etc. Marking chapter headings with a leading # and setting the "
"chapter XPath detection expression to \"//h:h1\" is the easiest way to have "
"a proper table of contents generated from a TXT document. You can learn more"
" about the Markdown syntax at `daringfireball "
"<https://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax>`_."
msgstr "calibre还支持通过名为Markdown的转换预处理器运行TXT输入。Markdown允许将基本格式添加到TXT文档中，如粗体、斜体、节标题、表格、列表、目录等。用前导#标记章节标题并将章节XPath检测表达式设置为“//h:h1”是从TXT文档生成正确目录的最简单方法。你可以在`daringfireball上了解更多关于Markdown语法的信息<https://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax>`_."

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:736
msgid ":guilabel:`Formatting style: None`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`格式化样式:无`"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:737
msgid ""
"Applies no special formatting to the text, the document is converted to HTML"
" with no other changes."
msgstr "不对文本应用任何特殊格式，文档在不进行其他更改的情况下直接转换为 HTML。"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:742
msgid "Convert PDF documents"
msgstr "转换PDF文档"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:744
msgid ""
"PDF documents are one of the worst formats to convert from. They are a fixed"
" page size and text placement format. Meaning, it is very difficult to "
"determine where one paragraph ends and another begins. calibre will try to "
"unwrap paragraphs using a configurable, :guilabel:`Line un-wrapping factor`."
" This is a scale used to determine the length at which a line should be "
"unwrapped. Valid values are a decimal between 0 and 1. The default is 0.45, "
"just under the median line length. Lower this value to include more text in "
"the unwrapping. Increase to include less. You can adjust this value in the "
"conversion settings under :guilabel:`PDF Input`."
msgstr "PDF文档是最难转换的格式之一。它们是固定的页面大小和文本放置格式。也就是说，很难确定一个段落在哪里结束，另一个段落从哪里开始。calibre将尝试使用可配置的“行解包因子”来解包段落。这是一个用于确定线应展开的长度的标尺。有效值是介于0和1之间的十进制数。默认值为0.45，刚好在中线长度下方。降低此值可在展开中包含更多文本。增加以包含更少。您可以在“PDF输入”下的转换设置中调整此值。"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:751
msgid ""
"Also, they often have headers and footers as part of the document that will "
"become included with the text. Use the :guilabel:`Search and replace` panel "
"to remove headers and footers to mitigate this issue. If the headers and "
"footers are not removed from the text it can throw off the paragraph "
"unwrapping. To learn how to use the header and footer removal options, read "
":ref:`regexptutorial`."
msgstr "此外，它们通常有页眉和页脚作为文档的一部分，这些页眉和页脚将包含在文本中。使用“搜索和替换”面板删除页眉和页脚以缓解此问题。如果没有从文本中删除页眉和页脚，则可以取消段落展开。要了解如何使用页眉和页脚删除选项，请阅读:ref:`regexptutorial`。"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:756
msgid "Some limitations of PDF input are:"
msgstr "PDF输入限制:"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:758
msgid "Complex, multi-column, and image based documents are not supported."
msgstr "该功能不支持复杂的、多栏布局以及基于图片的文档。"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:759
msgid ""
"Extraction of vector images and tables from within the document is also not "
"supported."
msgstr "此外，该功能也不支持提取文档中的矢量图形和表格。"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:760
msgid ""
"Some PDFs use special glyphs to represent ll or ff or fi, etc. Conversion of"
" these may or may not work depending on just how they are represented "
"internally in the PDF."
msgstr "某些 PDF 使用特殊字符（合字）来表示 ll、ff 或 fi 等字母组合。这些字符能否成功转换，取决于它们在 PDF 内部的具体表示方式。"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:761
msgid "Links and Tables of Contents are not supported"
msgstr "链接和目录不支持"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:762
msgid ""
"PDFs that use embedded non-Unicode fonts to represent non-English characters"
" will result in garbled output for those characters"
msgstr "如果 PDF 使用嵌入式非 Unicode 字体来表示非英语字符，会导致这些字符在输出结果中显示为乱码。"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:763
msgid ""
"Some PDFs are made up of photographs of the page with OCRed text behind "
"them. In such cases calibre uses the OCRed text, which can be very different"
" from what you see when you view the PDF file"
msgstr "某些 PDF 页面是由扫描的页面经过 OCR 处理的文本构成的。在这种情况下，calibre 会使用这些 OCR 文本，但它们可能与您在查看 PDF 文件时所见的内容大相径庭"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:764
msgid ""
"PDFs that are used to display complex text, like right to left languages and"
" math typesetting will not convert correctly"
msgstr "用于显示复杂文本（如从右向左书写的语言和数学排版）的 PDF 无法正确转换"

#: ../../../__w/calibre/calibre/manual/conversion.rst:766
msgid ""
"To re-iterate **PDF is a really, really bad** format to use as input. If you"
" absolutely must use PDF, then be prepared for an output ranging anywhere "
"from decent to unusable, depending on the input PDF."
msgstr "再次重申：PDF 是一种极其糟糕的输入格式。如果您绝对必须使用 PDF，那么请做好心理准备，输出效果可能从“尚可”到“完全不可用”不等，这完全取决于输入的 PDF 文件本身。"

